Welcome Home to Cherry lane Apartments
Find your new home at Cherry lane Apartments in Philadelphia. This community has much to offer its residents including its convenient location near some of the best dining and shopping that Meridian has to offer like The Philadelphia Towne and More. Cherry lane's unique and cozy floorplan with the features of a newly renovated apartment including Stainless Steel Appliances, new flooring, new paint, and washer and dryer in each unit. Let the knowledgeable leasing staff show you everything this community has in store. Experience a better way of living at Cherry lane Apartments.
